flowchart TD
    A([Open a lead with an inbound email]) --> B[Click 'Draft reply']
    B --> C[Pick reply type + tone]
    C --> D[Trigger fresh availability sync]

    subgraph BROWSER [In the browser - Do or Wait]
        D --> E[Read live availability + pricing from Firestore]
        E --> F[Run matcher - deterministic JS, no LLM]
        F --> G[Load per-lead Profile profile_md]
        G --> H[Send: email + reply type + tone + matched units + pricing + house style + profile + chat history]
    end

    subgraph SERVER [Server side - holds the API key]
        H --> I[Cloudflare Worker or n8n]
        I --> J[Call LLM - Claude Sonnet 4.6]
        J --> K[Return draft + optional profile-update suggestion]
    end

    K --> L[Draft appears in editable panel]
    L --> M{Refine it?}
    M -->|Yes - type an instruction| H
    M -->|No| N{Profile update suggested?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Review diff and accept] --> P
    N -->|No| P[Save]
    P --> Q[Write draft to lead thread]
    P --> R[Push draft to Outlook for review/send]
    Q --> S([Done - human reviews and sends])
    R --> S
